538
00:31:21,944 --> 00:31:24,086
Jason. C'est bon.

539
00:31:26,701 --> 00:31:27,815
Kevlar.

540
00:31:29,886 --> 00:31:30,706
Cool.

541
00:31:31,238 --> 00:31:32,622
T'en as un pour moi ?

542
00:31:34,143 --> 00:31:35,687
